                                        2973
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "We proposed a new light- field acquisition method that takes advantage of coded- aperture imaging and an event camera. Although the measurement on the camera can be completed in a single exposure, our method is theoretically quasiequivalent to the baseline coded- aperture imaging method."
                                }
                            ]
